{"tid":1590980,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傳中國要「一帶一路」寫入安理會決議 威脅動用否決權","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T08:26:49.000Z","uid":144372,"like":11,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"a267a21e7090e629ed398d0531b43bdd417eeff5","tid":1590980,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2919332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2919332&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ef8f3d86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2919332&h=cfce3ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2919332</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕聯合國安理會在本週二一致同意延長「聯合國駐阿富汗援助團」（UNAMA）任務決議案，但中國傳出曾在會議期間，一度威脅若決議沒寫入中國一帶一路計畫，將否決該決議。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，成立於2020年的「聯合國駐阿富汗援助團」在2016年、2017年和2018年授權任務的決議中，都包含歡迎和推動中國一帶一路計畫的內容，然而美國和部分安理會成員曾表示，不能再接受一帶一路被寫入決議，因此今年3月的決議中未提及一帶一路。<br />\n<br />\n而在經過本週二（17）的投票後，新決議並未提及一帶一路，據《共同網》，安理會消息人士透露，中國一度在會議中威脅，如果沒有在決議中寫入一帶一路項目，中國將否決該決議。而1項決議若要通過，需要9票贊成，且美國、中國、法國、俄羅斯和英國不得否決。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐聯合國大使克拉夫特（Kelly Craft）在會議中表示，「聯合國駐阿富汗援助團」的任務已經更新，以應對阿富汗的新發展，但也指出，該援助團無法被賦予更強的實質性任務，原因在於有安理會成員堅持在字詞上強調國家政治優先事項，而不是能最有效幫助阿富汗人民和政府的方式。<br />\n<br />\n中國常駐聯合國代表張軍則稱，很遺憾部分國家拒絕保留先前達成共識的決議文本。<br />\n<br />\n「聯合國駐阿富汗援助團」目前正協助阿富汗籌備9月28日的選舉，並正在推動阿富汗政府與塔利班之間的和平談判。"},{"pid":"e6992a92672f36d99c0364db5804b8a7f3f12049","tid":1590980,"uid":67454,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"踢支共出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34bdbcc879e16b72383e44fcd4c35d87895771f","tid":1590980,"uid":39365,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"e6992a92672f36d99c0364db5804b8a7f3f12049","tid":1590980,"uid":67454,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"踢支共出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"中共唔自己退出, 其他國家根本踢唔走佢, 同WTO一樣, 真係ON9制度"},{"pid":"b6ddc0b588b15485d4cda254da993fea88a7c453","tid":1590980,"uid":99962,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"聯合國係廢既"},{"pid":"2440ecc3d75a12e96f2a137c36b5729b8b675707","tid":1590980,"uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"UN汁咗佢啦"},{"pid":"5445463def0709840112c497ffba59382e422c62","tid":1590980,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好援助囉"},{"pid":"9e7b8e9a95633f3e713cf76ea0a2c9894c60a4b2","tid":1590980,"uid":69568,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e34bdbcc879e16b72383e44fcd4c35d87895771f","tid":1590980,"uid":39365,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"e6992a92672f36d99c0364db5804b8a7f3f12049","tid":1590980,"uid":67454,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"踢支共出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"中共唔自己退出, 其他國家根本踢唔走佢, 同WTO一樣, 真係ON9制度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"當年ROC點敗走"},{"pid":"3cd06b63833ad08556c9be46ab002a0840b59632","tid":1590980,"uid":41116,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"寫左咪美國否決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b829588afa9fdcbe6be51f93d73812695c4f4b","tid":1590980,"uid":282347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:30:43.000Z","msg":"League of Nations<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Chinazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Chin